<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/229> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #229" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 3.31.1; Diod. 12.4.1; Fast. Cap. (names entire); Dion. Hal. 10.31.1; Censorin. DN 17, 10; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; cf. CIL 6.32326, line 14; Degrassi 24f., 93, 362f. On Valerius, see Münzer, Gent. Val. 49, no. 45." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/228> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #228" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "In Diod. Valerius receives the cognomen Lactuca, but in Pliny (NH 19.59) and in Fast. Cap. on 356 the form is Lactucinus." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/219> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #219" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Another tradition keeps Volscius continuously in office from 461 to 457. See these years." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/218> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #218" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Continued the prosecution of M. Volscius Fictor for false witness against K. Quinctius (Liv. 3.25.2-3, and 29.6; cf. Dion. Hal. 10.23.4, and 24.3). On T. Quinctius, see Lübker no. 1, on Valerius, Münzer, Gent. Val. 49, no. 45." .
